/'
Class Diagram – Basic definitions

Purpose:
Focuses on the internal structure of a single class, illustrating
attributes, methods, and visibility modifiers.

*Visibility:
- - : private (accessible only within the class)
- # : protected (accessible to subclasses)
- + : public (accessible from anywhere)

*Members:
- Attributes: Data fields with types
- Methods: Functions with parameters and return types
'/

